{"tid":2476476,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Uber Eats司機遇2少女劫車 暴衝翻覆驚悚片曝！他掛車門噴飛慘死","createTime":"2021-04-05T13:55:31.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T03:43:45.000Z","uid":224066,"like":8,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"fbb1b86395f0b9512e39a8e80ba62430f337d006","tid":2476476,"uid":224066,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T13:55:31.000Z","msg":"美國華盛頓發生劫車事件，在目擊者錄下的驚悚影片中，一名Uber Eats司機喊道，「報警！她們是小偷，這是我的車。」而在坐在車內的是2名未成年少女，然而，少女竟突然猛踩油門，暴衝的車輛在大街上奔馳，但幾秒後便傳來巨大撞擊聲響，目擊者隨即狂奔跟上，可惜受害司機已經倒地不起，送醫仍不治身亡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cf-images.us-east-1.prod.boltdns.net/v1/static/4368278029001/2a932446-8d61-4274-b763-907494143fab/e89a95f7-91f2-4111-b28e-e3d5accf3bb2/1280x720/match/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcf-images.us-east-1.prod.boltdns.net%2Fv1%2Fstatic%2F4368278029001%2F2a932446-8d61-4274-b763-907494143fab%2Fe89a95f7-91f2-4111-b28e-e3d5accf3bb2%2F1280x720%2Fmatch%2Fimage.jpg&h=d7f06b6c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根據CNN報導，犯案的分別是13歲、15歲的未成年少女，她們用電擊槍攻擊了66歲Uber Eats司機安瓦爾（Mohammad Anwar），並試圖劫走他的車輛。根據目擊者拍攝的影片顯示，安瓦爾遇襲後求助喊道，「報警！她們是小偷，這是我的車。」目擊者請求一旁路人協助報警，安瓦爾同時整個人掛在車門上，想把坐在駕駛座的少女趕出車外。<br />\n<br />\n然而，少女卻突然猛踩油門，車輛隨即暴衝，在街道上飛快奔馳，卻在右轉T字路口後失控翻覆，目擊男子聽見巨大撞擊聲響後，趕忙狂奔追上，遺憾的是，安瓦爾早已被撞飛到人行道上，整個人倒在血泊中，送醫後不治身亡。當時正巧有數名美國國民兵目睹車禍現場，他們將少女們從側翻的車輛殘骸中拉了出來，並要求所有人後退，以免發生車輛爆炸。<br />\n<br />\nA Pakistani-American Uber Eats driver was killed when two girls aged 13 and 15 tried to carjack his car in Washington DC <a href=\"http://pic.twitter.com/whYKcPlChh\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.twitter.com%2FwhYKcPlChh&d=Ai36%2FzMZEIUB39LyUGzRLf%2BqeKGcMvuhkm4gAZs5aLs%3D&h=df9065de\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">pic.twitter.com/whYKcPlChh</a> &mdash; TRT World (@trtworld) March 27, 2021<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R5UeGaAFkPc&amp;ab_channel=InsideEdition\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DR5UeGaAFkPc%26ab_channel%3DInsideEdition&d=Ai36%2FzMZEIUB39LyUGzRLf%2BqeKGcMvuhkm4gAZs5aLs%3D&h=3e53419e\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=R5UeGaAFkPc&amp;ab_channel=InsideEdition</a><br />\n影片最後還可以看見，身穿粉色上衣的犯案少女無視於躺在地上的安瓦爾，一邊走向翻覆的汽車，一邊大喊著她的手機還在車上，但隨即被國民兵制止。死者家屬表示，安瓦爾2014年從巴基斯坦移民美國，如今卻留下了愛妻、3名子女與4名孫子女，獨自離世。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，由於嫌犯年齡關係，少女們的姓名未被公開，2人都將面臨重罪謀殺與持械劫車的指控。家屬在GoFundMe募款網站上為安瓦爾的遺孀籌措後事費用，據網頁上說明，這位Uber Eats司機是全家的經濟支柱，事發當時安瓦爾正在工作、養家餬口，卻在一場令人髮指的暴力事件中不幸罹難。"},{"pid":"51d51a06c44084ce2da174f038d75521d19e61cb","tid":2476476,"uid":252045,"like":14,"dislike":4,"score":10,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:00:06.000Z","msg":"依家啲細路...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n世界發生咩事"},{"pid":"9dd8247d3dcc3b82ba2b5c62c9adaeb773a21551","tid":2476476,"uid":53672,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:01:53.000Z","msg":"個阿叔心軟 唔係一拳窩埋去就ok"},{"pid":"502f8d980403a5a4eed914efccc3e8f621b97be8","tid":2476476,"uid":4783,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:03:39.000Z","msg":"又係黑人黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以唔講係咩人種<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果係白人一定大大隻字寫話係白人少女<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nThe suspects were both young black girls"},{"pid":"75f3e4fca6b457f9ee27570eb1d2571f4ee0bd82","tid":2476476,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:04:36.000Z","msg":"個兩個細路如果係黑人，話唔定唔會被告"},{"pid":"47986b4e2aa8a19af5bb0ad8f23b4e3dfe827409","tid":2476476,"uid":364798,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"75f3e4fca6b457f9ee27570eb1d2571f4ee0bd82","tid":2476476,"uid":141151,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:04:36.000Z","msg":"個兩個細路如果係黑人，話唔定唔會被告"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-05T14:05